$interpreted: Crushfang: That child has quite high standards. Certainly took a while, but finally found lovely partner, I see.
Dagger: You saying Dumb Bear has high standards?
Crushfang: It's the bride I'm speaking about.
Dagger: Eh? You know that Jasmine girl?
Crushfang: In fact, you know her as well~

Handsome Bear: Dumb Bear is finally marrying ugly cousin.
Next wedding shall be between me and Miss Rose!
Young Master Bear: No, it should be between ME and Miss Rose!
Handsome Bear: Speaking of which, all the food in this banquet is prepared by the bride herself. I'm a bit impressed that Dumb Bear can eat such terrifying food.
Young Master Bear: Dumb Bear paired with ugly cousin, what a perfect combination. Hahaha.
Dagger: Hey, you two! What did you just say!?
Dagger: Why you stopping me!?
Crushfang: At times like this, better to let one involved deal with them personally.

Dumb Bear Soldier: No wasting food!
Jasmine worked real hard to cook these dishes.
Handsome Bear: No way in hell would I eat such disgusting food.
Young Master Bear: I'm not eating it. What are you going to do? Scold me?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Pick it up, now.
Young Master Bear: I... I'm so sorry. I'll pick it up right away.
Handsome Bear: I will eat all of it, so please stop punching me in my face.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Now that's more like it. No wasting food.
Dagger: Dumb Bear, didn't know you such strong fighter?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Turns out I'm pretty strong fighter~~
Wedding Guest: The bride is here!
Wedding Guest: Miss Rose is truly a beauty...
Handsome Bear: Why is Miss Rose wearing a wedding dress?
Young Master Bear: Could it be... that she's going to use this opportunity to pick her partner right away?
Handsome Bear: Miss Rose, I knew you would choose me. There is not more handsome Bear than me in this world.
Young Master Bear: Miss Rose, just marry me. I will ensure you life of wealth and riches.
Rose: Bighammer, let's go. Ceremony is about to start.

Dumb Bear Soldier: Okay~~
Let's go eat big meal Jasmine prepared~~
Rose: I can cook it for you every day afterward.
Dumb Bear Soldier: Yippee~~~

Handsome Bear: D... Dumb Bear! You you you...
What did you just call Miss Rose!?
Young Master Bear: Why did you call her Jasmine!?
Dumb Bear Soldier: Huh? Didn't you guys meet her back in the desert?
Dumb Bear Soldier: She is Jasmine~~
Young Master Bear: How is this possible!?

Rose: Eh? Did I forget to tell you guys?
Jasmine is my nickname when I was still cub.
Handsome Bear: So you were lying to us when you told us that Jasmine is your cousin...
Young Master Bear: NO, that's impossible!

Young Master Bear: NO, that's impossible!
This is a trap! Someone definitely set us up!
Rose: I tell lies and trick people, to begin with. It's just who I am. You guys just went ahead and imagined a perfect me on your own.
Young Master Bear: Even so, you don't have to choose this idiot of all Bears!
Handsome Bear: That's right! Look at his dumb face, he doesn't pair well with your beauty no matter how you look at it!
Rose: Doesn't matter if you guys shower me with flowers or gems.
Rose: If you aren't even willing to have one bite of the food I cook, how are you going to spend the rest of your life with me? Oh, and another thing...
Rose: I remember I told you two that Rose has a bad temper, right? So, if anyone dares to call my husband dumb again, I will punch them.

Dumb Bear Soldier: But... I am Dumb Bear though?
They not wrong about that?
Rose: From now on, you're my big Dumb Bear and mine only.
Crushfang: ............
Crushfang: ............
Dagger: Why the weird smile? Creepy.
Crushfang: I was just thinking, in few years, would be your turn to have wedding.
Dagger: W... what nonsense you talking about! I'm not gonna get married!

Crushfang: Haha, wait until you meet girl you like.
Then we'll see if you can say those exact words again.
